title: The Sun's Babies
creator: Edith Howes
source: Librivox recording of a public-domain text
description: LibriVox recording of The Sun's Babies, by Edith Howes. Read by Laura Victoria. Charming stories and poems for young children about nature and the changes that occur with the seasons, weaving in life lessons throughout the stories. (Summary by Laura Victoria) For further information, including links to online text, reader information, RSS feeds, CD cover or other formats (if available), please go to the LibriVox catalog page for this recording. For more free audio books or to become a volunteer reader, visit LibriVox.org. M4B format available
